        <td><strong>Duck</strong></td>
        <td>Widely available</td>
        <td>Excellent first choice — rarely used in standard dog foods</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Venison</strong></td>
        <td>Moderate</td>
        <td>Very rarely seen in commercial foods — highly novel for most dogs</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Turkey</strong></td>
        <td>Widely available</td>
        <td>Good option IF your dog hasn't eaten turkey before (check current food labels)</td>
      </tr>
